CA CMS Collaboration
TI Measurement of the differential cross sections for the associated
   production of a W boson and jets in proton-proton collisions at root
   s=13 TeV

CA CMS Collaboration
TI Search for associated production of dark matter with a Higgs boson
   decaying to b(b)over-bar or gamma gamma at root s=13 TeV

CA CMS Collaboration
TI Search for new phenomena with the M-T2 variable in the all-hadronic
   final state produced in proton-proton collisions at root s=13TeV
